> Module OptTup

```catala-metadata
declaration structure Pair:
  data first content integer
  data second content money

declaration enumeration Choice:
  -- Yes content decimal
  -- No

declaration scope Calc:
  input maybe_amount content optional of money
  input pair content (integer, money)
  input mixed content optional of (Pair, Choice)
  input items content list of optional of integer
  output result content optional of decimal
  output combo content (Choice, optional of Pair)
```

```catala
scope Calc:
  definition result equals Absent
  definition combo equals (No, Absent)
```
